Description:

From single-celled to master the galaxy : develop your being you have created the universe.

Go through five stages of evolution Spore: cell , creature, tribe , civilization and space . Each stage has its own unique style, challenges and goals. You can play on your own : start on the stage and develop cells found in the body in a pool of nondescript intergalactic traveler or just start by creating tribes or civilizations on new planets. What you do with your universe - it's up to you.

In Spore , a plurality of powerful, yet easy -to-use creative tools that will create every element of your universe : creatures , vehicles , buildings, and even starships . While Spore - a game for one player, you have created beings are automatically made available to other players , which makes the number of worlds to explore and play virtually endless .
